menuconfig MCUMGR_CMD_NVS_MGMT
	bool "MCUmgr handlers for non-volatile storage management"
	depends on NVS
	select MGMT_MIN_DECODING_LEVEL_2
	help
	  Enables MCUmgr handlers for non-volatile storage management, which
	  allows for device configuration to be read and update. Note that
	  there is no security implied with the usage of this feature, all
	  NVS keys can be read or updated.
